    - A. Computer System
    - B. C-Sharp
    - C. Customer service
    - D. Computer Science
    CorrectAnswerIndex: 3
  - QuestionText: "C\xC2U 2: TRONG L\u0128NH V\u1EF0C AI, THU\u1EACT NG\u1EEE SOTA
