    - A. Self Organizing Tree Algorithm
    - B. State-of-the-Art
    - C. Sum of the Angles
    - D. Summits on the Air
    CorrectAnswerIndex: 1
  - QuestionText: "C\xC2U 3: TR\u01AF\u1EDENG KHOA HI\u1EC6N T\u1EA0I C\u1EE6A KHOA
