    Answers:
    - "A. Th\u1EA7y Mai Ti\u1EBFn D\u0169ng"
    - "B. C\xF4 Hu\u1EF3nh Th\u1ECB Thanh Th\u01B0\u01A1ng"
    - "C. Th\u1EA7y Ng\xF4 \u0110\u1EE9c Th\xE0nh"
    - "D. C\xF4 D\u01B0\u01A1ng Vi\u1EC7t H\u1EB1ng"
    CorrectAnswerIndex: 2
  - QuestionText: "C\xC2U 4: TRONG M\xD4N H\u1ECCC DSA, T\xCAN C\u1EE6A THU\u1EACT
