    Answers:
    - A. Binary Search
    - B. Dijkstra
    - C. Dinic
    - D. LCS
    CorrectAnswerIndex: 1
  - QuestionText: "C\xC2U 5: SINH VI\xCAN UIT S\u1EEC D\u1EE4NG LO\u1EA0I T\xC0I
      KHO\u1EA2N N\xC0O \u0110\u1EC2 \u0110\u0102NG NH\u1EACP V\xC0O H\u1EC6 TH\u1ED0NG
